{"title":"笔记本ArchLinux配置杂项","date":"2024-12-30T11:49:00.000Z","toc":true,"summary":"我的C302Archlinux的一些配置杂项","source":"_posts/我的C302Archlinux的一些配置杂项.md","raw":"---\ntitle: 笔记本ArchLinux配置杂项\ndate: 2024-12-30 19:49:00\ntags:\n    - linux\ntoc: true\nsummary: \"我的C302Archlinux的一些配置杂项\"\n---\n\n## 获取电池当前剩余电量\n\n>cat /sys/class/power_supply/BAT0/capacity\n更多详情见[此处](https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/Laptop#Battery_state)\n\n## 电脑屏幕背光控制\n\n详细描述[见此处](https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/Backlight)。\n>注意：最大亮度文件在`/sys/class/backlight/acpi_video0/max_brightness`,当更改亮度文件`/sys/class/backlight/acpi_video0/brightness`时，注意不要超过最大值。其中'acpi_video0'为ATI显卡控制下背光的文件所在文件夹，而intel控制下的背光文件夹为`intel_backlight`。\n\n## 触控板配置\n\n详细描述[见此处](https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/Libinput#Via_xinput_on_Xorg)\n\n```bash\n#显示电脑上可以由xinput控制的设备\nxinput list\n#显示某个设备(ID)可以更改的属性值(num)\nxinput list-props ID num\n#更改某个设备(ID1)的某个属性(ID2)属性值(num)\nxinput set-prop ID num\n```\n\n>对于C302我设置了Tapping Enable使用tap当做左右键点击，Natural scrolling Enable = 1启用正常的滚轮滑动，Scrolling Pixel Distance = 20，调慢了滚轮速度。\n\n## 估计陀螺仪和触摸屏旋转也是在这里设置，之后再说\n","slug":"我的C302Archlinux的一些配置杂项","published":true,"updated":"2024-12-31T15:12:07.429Z","_id":"cm5e1711b0009i4o22cm69x83","comments":true,"layout":"post","photos":[],"html":"<h2 id=\"获取电池当前剩余电量\"><a href=\"#获取电池当前剩余电量\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"获取电池当前剩余电量\"></a>获取电池当前剩余电量</h2><blockquote>\n<p>cat &#x2F;sys&#x2F;class&#x2F;power_supply&#x2F;BAT0&#x2F;capacity<br>更多详情见<a href=\"https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/Laptop#Battery_state\">此处</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"电脑屏幕背光控制\"><a href=\"#电脑屏幕背光控制\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"电脑屏幕背光控制\"></a>电脑屏幕背光控制</h2><p>详细描述<a href=\"https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/Backlight\">见此处</a>。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>注意：最大亮度文件在<code>/sys/class/backlight/acpi_video0/max_brightness</code>,当更改亮度文件<code>/sys/class/backlight/acpi_video0/brightness</code>时，注意不要超过最大值。其中’acpi_video0’为ATI显卡控制下背光的文件所在文件夹，而intel控制下的背光文件夹为<code>intel_backlight</code>。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"触控板配置\"><a href=\"#触控板配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"触控板配置\"></a>触控板配置</h2><p>详细描述<a href=\"https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/Libinput#Via_xinput_on_Xorg\">见此处</a></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#显示电脑上可以由xinput控制的设备</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">xinput list</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#显示某个设备(ID)可以更改的属性值(num)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">xinput list-props ID num</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#更改某个设备(ID1)的某个属性(ID2)属性值(num)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">xinput set-prop ID num</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>对于C302我设置了Tapping Enable使用tap当做左右键点击，Natural scrolling Enable &#x3D; 1启用正常的滚轮滑动，Scrolling Pixel Distance &#x3D; 20，调慢了滚轮速度。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"估计陀螺仪和触摸屏旋转也是在这里设置，之后再说\"><a href=\"#估计陀螺仪和触摸屏旋转也是在这里设置，之后再说\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"估计陀螺仪和触摸屏旋转也是在这里设置，之后再说\"></a>估计陀螺仪和触摸屏旋转也是在这里设置，之后再说</h2>","excerpt":"","more":"<h2 id=\"获取电池当前剩余电量\"><a href=\"#获取电池当前剩余电量\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"获取电池当前剩余电量\"></a>获取电池当前剩余电量</h2><blockquote>\n<p>cat &#x2F;sys&#x2F;class&#x2F;power_supply&#x2F;BAT0&#x2F;capacity<br>更多详情见<a href=\"https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/Laptop#Battery_state\">此处</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"电脑屏幕背光控制\"><a href=\"#电脑屏幕背光控制\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"电脑屏幕背光控制\"></a>电脑屏幕背光控制</h2><p>详细描述<a href=\"https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/Backlight\">见此处</a>。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>注意：最大亮度文件在<code>/sys/class/backlight/acpi_video0/max_brightness</code>,当更改亮度文件<code>/sys/class/backlight/acpi_video0/brightness</code>时，注意不要超过最大值。其中’acpi_video0’为ATI显卡控制下背光的文件所在文件夹，而intel控制下的背光文件夹为<code>intel_backlight</code>。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"触控板配置\"><a href=\"#触控板配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"触控板配置\"></a>触控板配置</h2><p>详细描述<a href=\"https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/Libinput#Via_xinput_on_Xorg\">见此处</a></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#显示电脑上可以由xinput控制的设备</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">xinput list</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#显示某个设备(ID)可以更改的属性值(num)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">xinput list-props ID num</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#更改某个设备(ID1)的某个属性(ID2)属性值(num)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">xinput set-prop ID num</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>对于C302我设置了Tapping Enable使用tap当做左右键点击，Natural scrolling Enable &#x3D; 1启用正常的滚轮滑动，Scrolling Pixel Distance &#x3D; 20，调慢了滚轮速度。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"估计陀螺仪和触摸屏旋转也是在这里设置，之后再说\"><a href=\"#估计陀螺仪和触摸屏旋转也是在这里设置，之后再说\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"估计陀螺仪和触摸屏旋转也是在这里设置，之后再说\"></a>估计陀螺仪和触摸屏旋转也是在这里设置，之后再说</h2>","path":"2024/12/30/我的C302Archlinux的一些配置杂项/","permalink":"http://example.com/2024/12/30/%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84C302Archlinux%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9B%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%9D%82%E9%A1%B9/","tags":[{"name":"linux","_id":"cm5e1710y0001i4o2374u2ny6","slug":"linux","path":"tags/linux/","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/linux/","length":6}],"categories":[],"prev":{"title":"ArchLinux安装指南备忘录","date":"2024-12-30T11:49:00.000Z","summary":"ArchLinux手动安装教程","slug":"ArchLinux安装指南备忘录","published":true,"updated":"2024-12-31T14:07:34.055Z","_id":"cm5e1710q0000i4o23plw9v92","layout":"post","photos":[],"excerpt":"","path":"2024/12/30/ArchLinux安装指南备忘录/","permalink":"http://example.com/2024/12/30/ArchLinux%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97%E5%A4%87%E5%BF%